name: Anakin Skywalker
Lore: '''You were right about me. Tell your sister ... you were right.''',
Text: 'If Luke is about to be lost from table and Vader is present, shuffle Reserve Deck and draw destiny. Add 6 if Emperor present. If total destiny > 12, Vader instead crosses to Light Side, Luke is not lost, opponent loses 6 Force, and Emperor (if present) is lost. (Immune to Sense.)',
